data.description: VERY motivated Sellers. Bring all offers! Welcome to Four Seasons at Terra Lago! Experience the epitome of luxury, active 55+ living in our exquisite Fox Canyon model. This stunning home is designed to offer you the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Step into a world of elegance as you enter the spacious living room adorned with high ceilings, large windows, and natural light cascading in. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living area to the modern kitchen, making it an ideal space for entertaining guests and creating unforgettable memories with your loved ones. The gourmet kitchen boasts top-of-the-line appliances, sleek granite countertops, and ample storage space. Whether you're an experienced chef or simply love cooking, this kitchen will surely inspire your culinary adventures. The master suite is a tranquil retreat, featuring a generously sized bedroom with a walk-in closet. The ensuite bathroom offers a luxurious soaking tub, a separate glass-enclosed shower, and dual sinks set in elegant vanities. The second bedroom, equally spacious with an adjacent full bathroom & a bonus room the size of a 3rd bedroom. A must see interior Costco closet too! Step outside to the private patio area, enjoy the fresh desert air, and unwind with a book in hand. As a resident of Four Seasons at Terra Lago, you'll have access to world-class amenities, including the resort-style pool, full fitness center, and many more. Make this your forever home.
